			<br/>Sacramento,<br/>
			CA 95829-3585</b></p>

	<p>Non-Profit: <strong>Tax ID 68-0360766</strong></p>

	<p><%= link_to 'Download an Order Form here', '/downloads/ncct_order_form.pdf', target: "_blank" %></p>
	
</div>


<% if current_user %>
<%= link_to 'New Product', new_product_path, class: "btn btn-default" %>
<% end %>
<% end %>

